data.eml:eml: Foraminifera study in Masfjorden, western Norway

Occurrence data of living benthic foraminifera (>63µm) in the Masfjord, collected in 2015. Samples were taken with a gravity corer. The data represent the occurrence of living benthic foraminifera in the upper sediment centimeters (0-2cm) of 3 replicates.
